Walter Byron (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Walter_Byron_(actor) 0 Walter Byron (11 June 1899 – 2 March 1972) was an English film actor. He starred opposite Gloria Swanson in the 1929 film Queen Kelly and appeared in 66 films between 1926 and 1942. Walter_Byron ( 11_June_1899 – 2_March_1972 ) was an_English_film_actor .
